messages.message:
@Serena Noted the feedback that the class creation experience is inconsistent between creating your first class (opting into classification) and creating any further classes after that.

In the designs, the first class you create does not show you suggestions, you simply have that text box to enter the name (since it's just naming that "default class" whose existence we weren't showing the user). If we had a suggested name, we could populate it in the text box, but if we don't we should just say like "Enter a class name".

I'll be taking another look at making this classification experience more consistent (soon!)
